# ChangeLog

## 0.3.1

- Write temporary files to /tmp to avoid permission issues

## 0.3.0

- Use Konflux to build the image
- Use [uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/) for Python dependency management
- Run container as non-root user
- Basic image tests

## 0.2.1

- Use `terraform apply` instead of `cdktf apply` in entrypoint.sh

## 0.2.0

- Included a generic entrypoint.sh  file

## 0.1.0

- Changed base image to er-base-cdktf:0.1.0
- Terraform AWS Provider 5.60.0
- FROM er-base-cdktf:0.1.0 (cdktf 0.20.8)

## 0.0.1

- Terraform AWS Provider 5.60.0
- FROM er-base-cdktf:0.0.1 (cdktf 0.20.8)
